@startuml
actor User
participant Frontend
participant "Food API" as FoodAPI
participant "Review API" as ReviewAPI
participant "Favorite API" as FavAPI
database PostgreSQL

User -> Frontend: Tim mon an
Frontend -> FoodAPI: GET /api/foods/search
FoodAPI -> PostgreSQL: query food_items
FoodAPI --> Frontend: food list
User -> Frontend: Gui review + favorite
Frontend -> ReviewAPI: POST /api/reviews/foods/:foodId
ReviewAPI -> PostgreSQL: insert review
Frontend -> FavAPI: POST /api/favorites/foods/:foodId
FavAPI -> PostgreSQL: upsert favorite
@enduml
